{"tid":1115525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他們曾說過……","createTime":"2019-04-19T08:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T08:57:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98c42e72a300e4b60cde0122622c308380ba3acb","tid":1115525,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190419/20659408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190419%2F20659408&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSYDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=0b0e1e8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190419%2F20659408&h=b51ff302\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190419/20659408</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他們曾說過&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190419/large/19ls8p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190419%2Flarge%2F19ls8p05.jpg&h=bcc4610f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n董建華1999年10月8日出席聯合商會午宴後，提及是時候放下六四包袱。<br />\n<br />\n「幾十年來，整個國內的發展有翻天覆地的變化，經濟持續增長、民生已有改善、社會穩定、國際地位日逐提升。為此，我覺得我們身為中國人應很驕傲。同時我亦說過，希望他們（民主黨）對國家更加了解。我亦和他們（民主黨）說過，現時是放下六四包袱的時候，因為這樣我們可以大家更努力為香港建設及為國家建設，一起去努力。」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;首任特首董建華於1999年10月8日談論民主黨應放下六四包袱  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：六四30年：前六四館長自號藍絲學與紅線共存<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n六四30年：前六四館長自號藍絲 學與紅線共存<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n蘋人誌：高端鏡頭裏的低端人口 (鄭天儀)<br />\n<br />\n六四30年：前六四館長自號藍絲學與紅線共存"}]}